---
description: Keep app, feature, hook, service, and component boundaries clean
globs: "{app,features,hooks,services,components}/**/*.{ts,tsx}"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Architecture Boundaries

- `app/` files are route/screens and composition only; keep domain logic minimal there.
- Put data parsing/loading in `services/`, not in UI components.
- Put interaction/state orchestration in `hooks/` or feature hooks.
- Keep reusable UI primitives in `components/ui/`; feature-specific UI stays in `features/`.
- Do not introduce new barrel-export hubs; prefer direct imports at call sites.
- Avoid new cross-layer shortcuts (for example, screen directly parsing XML/SVG).
- If a change crosses layers, keep interfaces typed and explicit.
